item.title: CVE-2020-11024|2024-08-04T11:21:14.238Z -- moonlight-stream -- moonlight
item.description: In Moonlight iOS/tvOS before 4.0.1, the pairing process is vulnerable to a man-in-the-middle attack. The bug has been fixed in Moonlight v4.0.1 for iOS and tvOS.
